@startuml seq_auth_logout
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: User Logout & Session Invalidation

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "User" as User
participant "React SPA" as Client
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Auth Service" as Auth
database "Redis (Cache)" as Redis

User -> Client : Click "Logout"
Client -> Gateway : POST /api/auth/logout \n(Header: Authorization Bearer JWT)
Gateway -> Auth : Route Request

Auth -> Auth : Verify JWT & Extract user_id
Auth -> Redis : DEL session:<user_id> \n(Token Blacklisting / Session Invalidation)

Auth -> Client : 200 OK (Logout Successful)
Client -> User : Clear Local Storage & Redirect to Login Screen
@enduml